title: #55 - Reacting to Dream’s Face Reveal
itunes:title: #55 - Reacting to Dream’s Face Reveal
description: On this podcast, Will Neff and Jackson Dahl come on as guests to talk about the latest news, trending topics, and anything else that comes to their mind. Starting with untold stories behind the scenes of the Logan Paul and Floyd Mayweather fight, the group goes on to talk and react to Dream's reportedly planned face reveal, El Salvador making Bitcoin an official currency, Adin Ross's leak of a groundbreaking gambling deal, Faze on the cover of Sports Illustrated, and more!
